{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"content":[{"anchor":"Overview","text":"Overview","type":"heading","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"As the library prepares for Swift 6 we are in the process of updating the library’s APIs for","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"sendability and isolation where appropriate, and doing so in a backwards compatible way. Prior"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"to version 1.14 of the library the ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store"},{"type":"text","text":" type has only ever been meant to be used on the"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"main thread, but that contract was not enforced in any major way. If a store was interacted with"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"on a background thread a runtime warning would be emitted, but the compiler had no knowledge of","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the type’s isolation.","type":"text"}]},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"That now changes in 1.14 where "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" is now officially ","type":"text"},{"code":"@MainActor","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":"-isolated. This has been"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"done in a way that should be 100% backwards compatible, and if you have problems please open a"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"http:\/\/github.com\/pointfreeco\/swift-composable-architecture\/discussions","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"."}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"However, if you are using "},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"strict"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"text":" concurrency settings in your app, then there is one circumstance","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"in which you may have a compilation error. If you are accessing the ","type":"text"},{"code":"store","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" in a view method or"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"property in Xcode <16, then you may have to mark that property as "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"text":":","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"syntax":"diff","code":[" struct FeatureView: View {","   let store: StoreOf<Feature>"," ","   var body: some View {","     \/\/ ...","   }"," ","+  @MainActor","   var title: some View {","     Text(store.name)","   }"," }"],"type":"codeListing"}],"kind":"content"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigrationGuides"]]},"abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"isActive":true,"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/Store"},{"text":" type is now officially ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"@MainActor"},{"type":"text","text":" isolated."}],"identifier":{"url":"doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.14","interfaceLanguage":"swift"},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/composablearchitecture\/migratingto1.14"]}],"schemaVersion":{"patch":0,"major":0,"minor":3},"seeAlsoSections":[{"identifiers":["doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17.1","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.17","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.16","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.15","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/documentation\/ComposableArchitecture\/MigratingTo1.13","doc:\/\/ComposableArchitecture\/